  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Play</h2>On the \"peaceful\" space station, a large number of out-of-control robots. You'll take control of the new E-201 and use your attributes, collect powerful skills, and match items to create a powerful Combo that can defeat a wide variety of enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/47d21a3ce0c499b9f1f08a41aed81868.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/47d21a3ce0c499b9f1f08a41aed81868.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/47d21a3ce0c499b9f1f08a41aed81868.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill Consumption</h2>E-201 can store fuel, hydrogen, electricity three kinds of energy. Skills costs energy, which varies from skill to skill. Use the powerful skill only by reasonable collocation of equipment and planning of energy use.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/da1b56269a6c088f011fbf9ddb499a89.webp?t=1771333242\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/da1b56269a6c088f011fbf9ddb499a89.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" class=\"bb_img\" width=720 height=320 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combined Effect</h2>There are combined  between skills and items, and raising the appropriate amount can activate the corresponding combined  effect. The combined  effect is a good boost to the player, often able to turn defeat into victory at the key moment of the battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/80abb4861c45d948229cf6c8b1668179.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/80abb4861c45d948229cf6c8b1668179.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Selective Reward/h2]<br>Carrying forward the traditional art of the roguelike game, players can choose the rewards of the next level as needed during the adventure: crystal (ready to buy), chip (collect and upgrade active skills), equipment (acquire passive skills).<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/a6b9570b3d4bf561bf1ebaea5ba00ea0.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/a6b9570b3d4bf561bf1ebaea5ba00ea0.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/a6b9570b3d4bf561bf1ebaea5ba00ea0.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Enemy</h2>A variety of out-of-control robots will attack you on your way through, and they will attack in different ways. Being familiar with their behavior patterns will help you beat them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/1390bb4cea0bf8f1028206680075c23f.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/1390bb4cea0bf8f1028206680075c23f.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/1390bb4cea0bf8f1028206680075c23f.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obstacle Challenge</h2>The trap of the horizontal board game is never absent. The challenge of the organ set a rich reward, the higher the risk, the greater the return, the more confident in their own operation of friends do not miss.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/e469818dcd12ff682b5af2f1fbf5868a.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/e469818dcd12ff682b5af2f1fbf5868a.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/e469818dcd12ff682b5af2f1fbf5868a.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerful Boss</h2>There is always a goalkeeper at each mark, they have particularly strong skills and attributes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/c41d41966b3f9400e08c39878fc3469e.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/c41d41966b3f9400e08c39878fc3469e.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/c41d41966b3f9400e08c39878fc3469e.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Galaxy Race/h2]<br>A race of speed and passion in a thrilling cosmic adventure. Winning the tournament unlocks more generous rewards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/235d21ad6504416f7626c9ffd00af3bc.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/235d21ad6504416f7626c9ffd00af3bc.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/235d21ad6504416f7626c9ffd00af3bc.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discord: <br>Twitter:Hang John</h2></h2>",
